---
# Card Component — Reusable card with title, description, and optional link
---
<article class="card">
    <div class="card-body">
        {if title}
            <h3 class="card-title">{title}</h3>
        {endif}
        {if description}
            <p class="card-desc">{description}</p>
        {endif}
        {if link}
            <a href="{link}" class="card-link">Read more →</a>
        {endif}
    </div>
</article>
